* Web Server

  SyMBA produces war files for upload onto a server such as {{{http://tomcat.apache.org/}Apache Tomcat}} or
  {{{http://glassfish.java.net/}Glassfish}}. Please ensure you have a suitable system in place for the upload of
  the SyMBA web archives.

